
VARIABLE ICDUMMY1
VARIABLE ICDUMMY2
VARIABLE ICDUMMY3
; Dummy variables for use in the CEVENT
VARIABLE MALBROKEN
; If Malthesia's statue is broken
;
MLIST 91 374 1 9        ; soldier
MLIST 91 375 1 3        ; citizen
MLIST 91 24  1 1        ; ghoul
MLIST 91 182 9 2        ; greater skeleton
MLIST 91 184 12 2        ; zovembie
MLIST 91 185 94 3       ; spectral lord
MLIST 91 186 68 3       ; rakshasha
MLIST 91 187 12 3        ; inseivax
MLIST 91 183 6 2        ; greater ghoul
; Generate soldiers, citizens
;
CEVENT 57 0 1078

; Low-probability echoes players will get:
RANDOM ICDUMMY2 1 24 1069
AFFECT ICDUMMY2
RANDOM ICDUMMY1 1 50 0
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 1
	ECHO ALL A soldier cries out in agony as his heart is pierced by a rusty steel blade.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 2
	ECHO ALL A soldier runs by, screaming at the top of his lungs.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 3
	IFVAR ICDUMMY2 = 1075
		ECHO ALL A soldier kicks over the body of one of the aelfen at the base of the statue.
	ELSE
		ECHO ALL The smell of burning wafts in from Bazaar Center.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 4
	ECHO ALL A soldier searches the body of a fallen citizen.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 5
	ECHO ALL A soldier wipes blood off of his brow as he passes by.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 6
	ECHO ALL The wind picks up, blowing snow and the smell of blood past you.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 7
	ECHO ALL You hear a woman's scream off in the distance.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 8
	ECHO ALL You hear someone screaming something around the Bazaar.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 9
	ECHO ALL A skeleton tears into a wolfling cub with its claws.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 10
	ECHO ALL A citizen swings her mace, shattering the bones of a skeleton.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 11
	ECHO ALL You catch a soldier pulling his sword from the chest of a young highlander.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 12
	ECHO ALL A murg works herself into a frenzy and begins to foam at the mouth.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 13
	ECHO ALL Several soldiers pull away the bodies of their fallen comrades.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 14
	ECHO ALL You hear a horrid wail off in the distance.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 15
	ECHO ALL You hear shrieking from across the city.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 16
	IFVAR ICDUMMY2 < 1551
                ECHO ALL An old man is trampled by several sentries running towards the Keep.
	ELSE
		ECHO ALL An old woman is pushes aside by several soldiers making their way towards the Bazaar.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 17
	ECHO ALL Several citizens yell something to each other as they rush past you.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 18
	IFVAR ICDUMMY2 = 1075
		ECHO ALL A citizen waves her fist at the statue of Malthesia and snarls.
	ELSE
		ECHO ALL A wolfling mourns the loss of her cub, still carrying its lifeless body in her arms.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 19
	ECHO ALL Faint howling noises come from the direction of Shartan.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 20
	IFVAR ICDUMMY2 < 1081
		ECHO ALL War cries sound across the Bazaar.
	ELSE
                ECHO ALL War cries sound from the Bazaar.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 21
	ECHO ALL A frightened child cowers in the shadows.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 22
	 ECHO ALL You hear chanting from further down the street.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 23
ECHO ALL A soldier bellows, "Glory to Malthesia's army!"
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 24
	 ECHO ALL A huge gust of wind blows, nearly knocking you over.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 25
	 ECHO ALL A mechanoid rushes by, carving a path through the undead soldiers.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 26
	 ECHO ALL One of the soldiers grabs a drakin by the neck, pulls her head back and thrusts his sword through her chest.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 27
	 ECHO ALL A wolfling snarls at a sentry.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 28
	 ECHO ALL An arrow flies across the area, hitting a sentry in the chest.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 29
	 ECHO ALL A maniacal laughter sounds throughout the city.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 30
     ECHO ALL A sentry falls at the hands of a young murg.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 31
     ECHO ALL You hear the beating of a drum off in the distance.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 32
	 ECHO ALL Sparks fly through the air as an enchanter speaks an incantation.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 33
	 ECHO ALL The air grows colder.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 34
	 ECHO ALL You feel a deathly chill fill the area.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 35
	 ECHO ALL The ground shakes violently beneath your feet.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 36
     ECHO ALL You hear the boom of thunder off in the distance.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 37
	 ECHO ALL Lightning flashes across the sky, followed by the sound of thunder.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 38
	 ECHO ALL Forks of brilliant white lightning play across the sky.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 39
         ECHO ALL A group of soldiers surround someone and begin beating him mercilessly.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 40
	 ECHO ALL You hear crying.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 41
	 ECHO ALL A psionicist chants as he projects his mental energy at a skeleton.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 42
	 ECHO ALL A psionicist concentrates intently, creating a wall of force around her body.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 43
	 IFVAR ICDUMMY2 = 1705
		  ECHO ALL Some birds which vaguely resemble vultures pick at the aelfen bones scattered before you.
	 ELSE
		  ECHO ALL Some birds which vaguely resemble vultures pick at the decaying flesh of a fallen sentry.
	 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 44
	 ECHO ALL You hear a pained "SQUAK" off in the far reaches of your mind.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 45
	 ECHO ALL You get the distinct sensation that something is watching over you.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 46
	 ECHO ALL The stench of rotting garbage wafts by.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 47
	 ECHO ALL A sentry hisses as it delivers a coup-de-grace to its victim.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 48
	 ECHO ALL A drakin collapses, exhausted.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 49
	 ECHO ALL A mechanoid rushes by, stripped of all its skin, but otherwise unperturbed.
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 50
	 ECHO ALL Your soul is chilled as you hear a deep, maniacal laughter.
ENDIF
;IFVAR ICDUMMY1 =
;    ECHO ALL
;ENDIF
; High-probability echoes players will get:
RANDOM ICDUMMY2 1 24 1069
STRCVT 0 ICDUMMY2
; AFFECT 482
; ECHO ALL Sending high-probability ECHO ALL to room %0.
AFFECT ICDUMMY2
RANDOM ICDUMMY1 1 8 0
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 1
	ECHO ALL A citizen slashes at a soldier with his sword.
	SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 2
	 ECHO ALL A soldier slashes at a citizen with his sword.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 3
	 ECHO ALL Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of a soldier.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 4
	 ECHO ALL Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of a citizen.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 5
	 ECHO ALL Your thoughts are jarred as you sense the death of a sentry.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 6
	 ECHO ALL A sentry gestures into the air.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 7
	 ECHO ALL A citizen slashes at a soldier with her sword.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
IFVAR ICDUMMY1 = 8
	 ECHO ALL A soldier slashes at a citizen with her sword.
         SPELL 406
ENDIF
;
AFFECT 482
; Affect 482 just for safety.
;
MACRO 97
IFPREVERB CAST -1
	; 225->318
	IFVAR SPELLNUM = 225
                ; Invis. -> BRII
                EQUAL SPELLNUM 317
	ENDIF
	; 504->312
	IFVAR SPELLNUM = 504
		; Call Animal->Wail of the Banshee
		EQUAL SPELLNUM 312
	ENDIF
	; 102->105
	IFVAR SPELLNUM = 102
		; Mystic Armor->Globe of Protection
		EQUAL SPELLNUM 105
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVAR RAC ! 0
	RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5000 0
	IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
		DAMAGEALL BODYONLY 20 Suddenly the air around you bursts into flames!
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB FLY -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER The wind is too strong for you to take off from here.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WEATHER -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER It is winter.
	ECHO PLAYER It is snowing heavily.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB TIME -1
	CLEARVERB
	ECHO PLAYER It is the Day of Rebellion.
	ECHO PLAYER You are unable to determine what time it is.
ENDIF





REGIONDEF 13 EXTRAPLANAR
REGIONDEF 13 WEATHER
REGIONDEF 13 SEASONS
REGIONDEF 13 WINTERTEMP -5
REGIONDEF 13 SUMMERTEMP -5
REGIONDEF 13 SPRINGTEMP -5
REGIONDEF 13 AUTUMNTEMP -5
REGIONDEF 13 PRECIPITATION -75
REGIONDEF 13 TELEPORT ALLOWED
REGIONDEF 13 SUMMONING ALLOWED
REGIONDEF 13 WELLOFLIFE ALLOWED
REGIONDEF 13 FIRE 90
REGIONDEF 13 COLD 150
REGIONDEF 13 ELECTRIC 3
REGIONDEF 13 ENCHANTMOD -10






NUMBER 1070
NAME City Wall
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The massive gateway stands before you, unguarded and open. To the west, a wide
street plunges into the city's heart, where people of many races go about
their own business. Several of the city's inhabitants dressed in rags huddle
around a small fire both to keep themselves from freezing to death, and to
keep them away from the fighting occurring over the rest of the town.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 1071
ITEM 0 1567 ADJ1=358
; Snow
ITEM 1 763 VAL1=700 VAL2=2087 OPEN
; Gate
CALL 97
;
NUMBER 1071
NAME Main Street
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
People in this wide street sidestep to avoid each other, careful not to make
eye contact with either you or the City Guard. Those fortunate enough to be
fully clothed, walk by with their coats pulled tightly around them. Those who
are somewhat less fortunate, scuttle by you partially dressed in tattered
rags.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 1070
EXIT W 1072
ITEM 0 1567 ADJ1=95
; Snow
CALL 97
;
NUMBER 1072
NAME Bazaar East
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
Here at the eastern edge of the Bazaar, you can make out the relatively
disorganized fighting that is going on in the rest of the city's center and
its various side streets. What was once the Sojourner's Hospice lies to the
side, its entrance boarded up.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 1073
EXIT E 1071
EXIT S 1077
EXIT SW 1076
EXIT W 1075
EXIT NW 1074
ITEM 0 1567 ADJ1=95
