;
NUMBER 1073
NAME Bazaar Northeast
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The citizens of this town that predominate elsewhere avoid this part of
the bazaar. A stone building, entirely colorless, displays only the words
"EXECUTION HEADQUARTERS" in block letters above a closed door. The
architecture is plain and looks completely functional. When your business is
death ensurance, it looks undignified to adorn your building with garish
decorations.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 1072
EXIT SW 1075
EXIT W 1074
ITEM 0 1567 ADJ1=358
; Snow
ITEM 1 65 VAL2=1074 VAL1=500 CLOSED LOCKED
; Door
CALL 97
;
