Gaunt highlanders and haggard wolflings peek out from behind debris which
serves as a barricade at the north end of the Bazaar. Whole buildings lie
overturned and demolished before you. You catch sight of a familiar-looking
sign that lies at your feet.
*DESCRIPTION_END
