It would appear that the Armourer's Guild is buying a surprisingly small
number of weapons from local adventurers these days. The debris that was once
the Guild lies in a relatively neat pile, around which various soldiers and
citizens engage in hand-to-hand combat. A gaping hole in the ground leads
downwards.
*DESCRIPTION_END
