NUMBER 1075
NAME Bazaar Center
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
You revel in the tumult as the center of the Bazaar overwhelms your senses
with the awful stench of burning flesh and the sights of hundreds fighting
across the Bazaar. Remains of the recently destroyed aelfen population lie at
the base of several wooden poles arranged in a ring around an immense statue.
More and more join their numbers as the fighting continues.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT N 1074
EXIT NE 1073
EXIT E 1072
EXIT SE 1077
EXIT S 1076
EXIT SW 1080
EXIT W 1079
EXIT NW 1078
ITEM 0 1567 ADJ1=95
; Snow
ITEM 1 1194
; Pole
ITEM 2 346
; Statue
CALL 97
IFPREVERB BREAK 2
	CLEARVERB
	EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
	ADD MALBROKEN 1
	IFVAR MALBROKEN = 1
		ECHO PLAYER You start hacking away at the statue.
		ECHO OTHERS %N starts hacking off bits of Malthesia's statue.
	ELSE
		IFVAR MALBROKEN = 3
			ECHO PLAYER As you strike the statue, one of its arms crumbles.
			ECHO OTHERS As %n strikes the statue, one of its arms crumbles.
		ELSE
			IFVAR MALBROKEN = 5
				ECHO PLAYER You chip Malthesia's nose off.
				ECHO OTHERS %N chipx the statue's nose off.
			ELSE
				IFVAR MALBROKEN = 8
					ECHO PLAYER As you strike Malthesia's head, it comes free and flies across the Bazaar, knocking a soldier unconscious.
					ECHO OTHERS As %n strikes the statue's head, it comes free and flies across the Bazaar, knocking a soldier unconscious.
				ELSE
					IFVAR MALBROKEN = 10
						ECHO PLAYER You succeed in completely destroying the statue.
						ECHO OTHERS The statue crumbles as %n hits it.
					ELSE
						IFVAR MALBROKEN > 10
							ECHO PLAYER You hack away at the remnants of the statue.
							ECHO OTHERS %N uselessly hacks away at the remnants of Malthesia's statue.
						ELSE
							ECHO PLAYER You hack away at the statue.
							ECHO OTHERS %N hacks away at the statue of Malthesia.
						ENDIF
					ENDIF
				ENDIF
			ENDIF
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
;
IFPREVERB LOOK 2
	CLEARVERB
	IFVAR MALBROKEN = 0
		ECHO PLAYER The statue is of Malthesia, larger than life, his arms raised over the fallen
		ECHO PLAYER body of an aelfen girl. A plaque below reads, "Malthesia, Lord of Andor".
	ELSE
		IFVAR MALBROKEN < 10
			IFVAR MALBROKEN < 1
				ECHO PLAYER Parts of the statue have been chipped away, but the statue still stands - Malthesia, with his arms raised over the fallen body of an aelfen girl.
			ELSE
				IFVAR MALBROKEN < 3
					ECHO PLAYER One of Malthesia's arms have been broken off.
				ELSE
					IFVAR MALBROKEN < 5
						ECHO PLAYER One of Malthesia's arms have been broken off, along with his nose.
					ELSE
						IFVAR MALBROKEN < 8
							ECHO PLAYER While nothing can be done about the aelfen girl, Malthesia's statue is missing an arm and its head.
						ELSE
							ECHO PLAYER The upper half of the statue has been completely destroyed.
						ENDIF
					ENDIF
				ENDIF
			ENDIF
		ELSE
			ECHO PLAYER Only the base of the statue now stands, around which lie several chunks of rock.
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
ENDIF
