NUMBER 1089
NAME First Street
REGION 13
CHANNEL 778
MONSTER_GROUP 91
CALL 33
*DESCRIPTION_START
The familiarity of the city overwhelms you here. You see the same homes that
exist in your Fayd, now twisted and in the hands of Malthesia's army elite.
Walking down First Street, you halfway expect to see children playing amongst
pristine homes and trees covered by pure-white snow. Instead, men and women in
chain mail trudge through red stained sludge. A path between two buildings
leads north towards what used to be Park Avenue, and First Street continues
over rubble to the southeast.
*DESCRIPTION_END
